{
  "page": "Night Lamp",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #DEDEE2;\">Night Lamp</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\nLighthouse</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Godric_Borrell_by_Borja_Pindado.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Godric Borrell by Borja Pindado.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f7/Godric_Borrell_by_Borja_Pindado.jpg/300px-Godric_Borrell_by_Borja_Pindado.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"240\" class=\"thumbborder\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f7/Godric_Borrell_by_Borja_Pindado.jpg/450px-Godric_Borrell_by_Borja_Pindado.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f7/Godric_Borrell_by_Borja_Pindado.jpg/600px-Godric_Borrell_by_Borja_Pindado.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>The Night Lamp and its <a href=\"/index.php/Keeper_of_the_Night_Lamp\" title=\"Keeper of the Night Lamp\">keeper</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Godric_Borrell\" title=\"Godric Borrell\">Godric Borrell</a>.<br />By Borja Pindado © Fantasy Flight Games</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Location</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Sisterton\" title=\"Sisterton\">Sisterton</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Sweetsister\" title=\"Sweetsister\">Sweetsister</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Vale_of_Arryn\" title=\"Vale of Arryn\">Vale of Arryn</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>Night Lamp</b> is a black tower, one of the beacons that burns along the shore of the <a href=\"/index.php/Three_Sisters\" title=\"Three Sisters\">Three Sisters</a>. It is located at <a href=\"/index.php/Sisterton\" title=\"Sisterton\">Sisterton</a> on <a href=\"/index.php/Sweetsister\" title=\"Sweetsister\">Sweetsister</a>. Along with the other beacons, it is supposed to warn of shoals and reefs and rocks and lead the way to safety. However, on stormy nights and foggy ones, some Sistermen use false lights to draw unwary captains to their doom.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Borrell\" title=\"House Borrell\">House Borrell</a> holds the title <a href=\"/index.php/Keeper_of_the_Night_Lamp\" title=\"Keeper of the Night Lamp\">Keeper of the Night Lamp</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Behind_the_Scenes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Behind the Scenes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Night_Lamp&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Godric_Borrell\" title=\"Godric Borrell\">Godric Borrell</a> intentionally turned off the Night Lamp to <a href=\"/index.php/Wrecker\" title=\"Wrecker\">wreck</a> ships. Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis Baratheon</a> threatened to hang Godric if he did it again.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Behind_the_Scenes\">Behind the Scenes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Night_Lamp&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Behind the Scenes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The Night Lamp may be a reference by <a href=\"/index.php/George_R._R._Martin\" title=\"George R. R. Martin\">George R. R. Martin</a> to <i><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Night_Lamp\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Night Lamp\">Night Lamp</a></i> by <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jack_Vance\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Jack Vance\">Jack Vance</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Night_Lamp&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://cantuse.wordpress.com/2014/08/28/the-night-lamp-revisited-the-wrath-of-the-old-and-the-new/\">The Night Lamp theory by Cantuse</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Night_Lamp&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_9\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 9\">Chapter 9</a>, Davos I.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403183437\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.050 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.200 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 347/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 9235/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 3148/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 292/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1060/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.130/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 5.3 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  190.369      1 -total\n 95.61%  182.005      1 Template:Infobox_settlement\n 95.22%  181.271      1 Template:Infobox\n  3.42%    6.502      3 Template:Ref\n  2.12%    4.030      3 Template:Ref/core\n  0.81%    1.542      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:11398-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403183437 and revision id 324824